INSERT INTO `cms_article` VALUES ('86', '', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//20160204/66081454569996917.png\" title=\"新闻快报1.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">阳历的2016年，但按照中国人的习俗，过了春节，才算是新的一年，所以我们跨年的脚步到现在也只是迈出了一半儿，真正新的一年，看来还是要等几天。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">今天是个平常的周日，因为最近项目很紧，所以白天依然在公司加班，对于互联网产品经理来说，这也是习以为常的一件事。下了班，总觉得好像少了点什么，也许是不甘心就这样度过一个周末吧，虽然天色已晚，但我还是来到三里屯的一家小酒馆里，来寻找一份属于周末的惬意。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这间小酒馆坐落在三里屯的一条胡同里，人也不多，并没有醉气熏天的吵闹，人们有的成对聊天，有的独自小酌，昏暗的灯光伴随着 Louis Armstrong 的音乐，吧台上摆着各式酒器，窗口处点着蜡烛，这样的氛围在这寒冷的冬天总是让人感到一阵暖意。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我坐在吧台的一个靠边的位子上，向调酒师点了一杯并不常喝的鸡尾酒，我很喜欢看调酒师潇洒的调酒动作，而且我认为调酒师就是这样一个自己和他人都可以乐在其中的工作。不一会儿，一杯鸡尾酒和一碟花生米就端到了我面前。小抿一口，很我喜欢这种味道。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“Fashion Capital，不错的选择。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">不知何时，我旁边的空位上坐着一个中年男人，他看上去文质彬彬的，瘦瘦的脸颊上托着一副黑框眼镜，“我也很喜欢喝这个酒，味道总是让人怀念。”他指着我手中的酒说。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“是么，看来您常来这个地方，但之前没见过您。”虽然我想一个人静静地坐会儿，但既然人家来聊天了，不理人家总是不礼貌的。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“我很少周末来，今天正好在附近有事，所以就来坐坐。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">不知道是不是看我没有接着往下说，它就继续说道“看你有些疲惫的样子，刚加完班？”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“是”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“周日也加班，你是做什么工作的？”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“产品经理”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“你们到底是做什么的？我最近总能听到这个职位。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我本想长篇大论地向他讲解我的工作内容，但转念一想，如果不是做这一行的，也很难明白我在讲什么，所以我就草草地说“你用微信吗？产品经理就是设计你在微信上怎么联系朋友，怎么微信付款的人。”老实讲，我并不喜欢这种回答方式，因为这个回答降低了产品经理的价值和贡献，但好像又想不出能够完整表达产品经理的工作而又能让对方明白的回答方式。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“哦？这听上去很有意思，我以前一直以为这是写代码程序的技术人员设计的。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我没想到他会这样接下我的话，因为以往我想别人这样讲解之后，对方总是会一知半解地应和，然后就转向下一个话题了，这样的对话，也让我起了性质。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“您这么说也不无道理，但这是一个理想的状态，实际工作和理想总是有差距的。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“什么是理想的工作状态？”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“理想的情况就是有一些同事，他们负责在网站或者 App 上搞活动或者发布内容，发现了一些问题，他们就召集了其他同事共同分析这个问题，然后提出了一个解决方案，他们拿着这个解决方案找到了技术部门的负责人，技术部门马上开会完善了这个解决方案，并将其拆分为了若干个功能点，同时技术负责人拿着这个方案找到了老板，老板认为方案可行并且给予大力支持，技术部门正式立项，开始了项目的开发，老板通知其他部门的负责人，要求加紧学习即将上线的新功能涉及的知识或工具，其他部门人员学习了新的知识和工具，公司全体员工配合得井井有条，随着技术开发的结束，这个问题被解决了，大家欢欣鼓舞，准备迎接下一个挑战。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“这不是你们的工作方式吗？听上去就应该这样。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“所以我说理想和现实是有差距的，您想象一下，一个公司的所有人员没有推脱责任、没有怠慢工作，所有人都为他人着想，这样的公司存在吗？肯定是不存在的。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“你说得也是。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“所以大部分的情况都是一些同事确实遇到了问题去找技术，但往往这些人的形容太过抽象，技术人员听得一头雾水，技术的专业术语，他们又听不懂，随着双方耐心的逐渐消耗，这件事要么不了了之，要么技术人员云里雾里地按照自己的理解把功能做了出来，最后也不会让用的人满意。还有，我刚才提到了老板会通知其他部门的人员的环节，这个环节的前提是老板有充足的时间来听技术人员解释，并且能够知道技术人员在说什么，其他部门的同事拥有强大的执行力，能够自我成长和学习。但实际情况却是，老板根本没有时间听解释，而且也不能保证公司里的所有员工都有很强的执行能力，所以综合以上两个例子，就需要有人首先能够理解问题的真正所在，并将这个问题用技术的语言解释给技术部门的同事听，并在使用者的角度上思考怎么做才是合理且好用的，还要能够锲而不舍地蹲守老板，用几句话让老板明白这个问题的严重性，并厚着脸皮地去找其他部门的负责人和相关人员讲述需要他们配合的地方，以及对涉及的知识或者工具做一个初步讲解，并且能在后期做到及时地解答和帮助。这些都在产品经理的工作范围内，基本上产品经理就是保证整个产品或公司能够有序运转起来的那个人，只要能够达到这个目的，任何事情都是产品经理的工作。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">不知是不是被我的话绕晕了，他若有所思地喝了一口自己的酒，“听你这么说，产品经理这个职位好像大部分的工作都是在沟通，而且要能承受住很大的压力。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这种回答真实让我有些吃惊，让我对眼前这位戴着黑框眼镜，又瘦瘦的中年男人刮目相看。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“您的总结很到位，这是我听过最好的回答。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">他啜饮了几口自己杯中的酒，又说“你喜欢自己的工作吗？”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“喜欢。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“你喜欢这样的生活吗？”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">他这么一问我还真不知道怎么回答，我很热爱我的工作，但我知道生活中除了工作还应该有点别的，毕竟彩色照片总比黑白照片来得精彩。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">他见我没有回答，说：“我以前和你一样，把工作看成是生活中的大部分，但时间久了，我发现工作永远是做不完的，但时间总是有限的，所以我决定在生活的其他方面多投入时间，比如多陪陪家人，培养一个兴趣爱好。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“老实讲我不知道怎么回答您的问题，我明白您的意思，也知道怎样的生活方式是好的，但生活中往往缺乏这种选择的权利，我们总是不得不接受一些事实。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“嗯，你说得很对，我并不是说不看重自己的工作，毕竟热爱自己的工作也是一种优秀的品质，我的意思是要在工作和生活之前找到平衡，老实讲我能看出你是一个认真负责的人，但想要长期做好一件事情，首先要学会享受生活。“</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">酒馆里的灯光依然让人感到温暖，调酒师优雅地为客人们调制鸡尾酒，我喝了一口自己的鸡尾酒，思索着如何进行下面的对话。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">他把自己杯中的酒一饮而尽，说：”时间差不多了，我要走了，希望下次还可以见到你。“</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我看着这个男人离开的背影，心里回荡着他对我说的话，是啊，一个好的产品经理要学会享受生活，毕竟我们的所有创意和灵感也是从生活中得来的，我们的工作是为了让人们的生活变得丰富而有趣，但这个前提是我们自己的生活也要是生动的。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这样的对话在生活中也许有很多，虽然短暂，却很有意义。我们彼此探讨，彼此交流，彼此说出内心真实的想法，我们也是在这样一次又一次的对话中逐渐成长的。因为往往只有在别人的指点下，我们才会意识到那些我们明明知道，但却总是忽视的问题。所以好好生活吧，好好享受现在的时光。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">忽然想起《男人帮》里的一段话：</p><blockquote style=\"width: 800px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0px; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.7999992370605px;\">我们处在一个瞬息万变的世界。光有爱情是不够的，有些东西，你以为拥有得理所应当，但当你失去的时候，才知道原来并没有资格，只是上天像游客一样。在你身边逛了一次。幸好有这样的一次，让我知道我并不只是我，我还有更强大的自己，在未来等着我，而每一个男人的心中有多少的焦虑，有多少的恐慌，因为这个世界上这么多的狼，我这只牧羊犬只好放弃自己的温顺，向着这个世界放出最耀眼的光。</p></blockquote><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/58\\86.html', '', '0', '1549');
INSERT INTO `cms_article` VALUES ('87', '', '<p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">微博上看过一篇文章，讲的是我们身边的朋友，即使是渣渣也有吊炸天的一面：</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>英语只知道WTF可能画画很厉害</p></li><li><p>跟人说话就脸红可能写代码是高手</p></li><li><p>成绩一塌糊涂，但是确实汽车知识的行家</p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">··· ···</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>我们为什么要写“干货”？因为我们每个人都是学霸。</strong>我们每个人都有自己熟悉、热爱的知识和经验领域。这些知识就藏在我们的脑海里，我们每天潜意识都在应用，但是我们却不知道这些如果分享出来，会给别人多大的价值。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">小六也是一个偶然的机会，写了一篇PPT的分享，才发现原来我习以为常的东西，很多小伙伴却并不知道。当我把自己的经验写出来，发现居然让很多小伙伴能得到启发和帮助，哦，原来这就是我的经验呀。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114203.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278377 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114203.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570576913.jpg\" alt=\"QQ20160131114203\" width=\"444\" height=\"257\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">每个人都有自己学霸的一面</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>除了能帮助别人，分享的过程也是对自己的知识进行一次重新归纳整理</strong>。很多时候可能是因为和别人聊天的时候的一句话，或者一个问题，会让你重新思考你的经验。而写文章是最好的一种思考的过程。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>今天小六就结合自己的经验和看过的书，和大伙聊一聊如何从零开始写出一篇知识性文章（干货）。</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/195046-755be008740ade23.png\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\"  wp-image-278370 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/195046-755be008740ade23.png\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577013.png\" alt=\"195046-755be008740ade23\" width=\"686\" height=\"321\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">本文的结构</p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-bottom-style: solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">一、知识的收集和整理</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">分享并不是凭空而来的，在分享之前，你需要对自己现有的知识进行收集，整理和归类。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">当你要收藏一个公众号文章的时候，你就可以想想了，这个文章是属于我的专业领域的么？还是专业领域中基础的，还是通用类的？</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114144.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278375 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114144.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577115.jpg\" alt=\"QQ20160131114144\" width=\"441\" height=\"343\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">收集来的知识属于哪个区域的？</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">收集是一个日常的活动，注重日常素材的积累，会让你在写干货的时候，准备充足的材料。</p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-bottom-style: solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">二、规划</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">好啦，不管怎样你终于鼓起勇气准备写干货啦！</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">没有什么头绪？没关系，我们来看看下面的步骤能不能帮到你：</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">1.确定主题</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114136.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278374 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114136.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577175.jpg\" alt=\"QQ20160131114136\" width=\"535\" height=\"253\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">找到自己得心应手的主题</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>我对什么题材感兴趣？</p></li><li><p>就个人而言，我对什么有兴趣？</p></li><li><p>我的专业领域是什么？</p></li><li><p>我从生活中学到了哪些经验？</p></li><li><p>我的目标读者对哪些东西感兴趣？</p></li></ul><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">2.选择话题</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114129.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278373 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114129.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577245.jpg\" alt=\"QQ20160131114129\" width=\"344\" height=\"375\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">选择主题中的话题</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>列出话题列表</strong>，比如知识管理有6个步骤：提问，收集，整理，分享，利用和创新，那知识管理就可以有6个话题。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>逐步缩小</strong>，从这个主题的一堆话题中，缩小范围，当前你专注和应用的是哪些？</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>聚焦</strong>，然后从中挑选一个你最想在当下整理和分享的，记住哦，分享干货是帮助他人，也是有利于自己当下做的事情。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>限定1500-3000字，</strong>分享一个话题的文章，文字最好在1500-3000字上下，现在碎片化的时候，受众很难有耐心看完一篇3000字的文章。所以如果你感觉这个话题一篇文章可能3000字讲不完，可以考虑将话题拆分，分成一百单八回，轮着讲~</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">3.弄清目标</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">虽然我一直强调分享的好处，当你确定话题之后，分享的要达到的目标还是需要考量的。</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>我想教读者什么？</p></li><li><p>我想分享哪些经验？</p></li><li><p>我想迈入新的领域么？</p></li><li><p>我希望如何成名？</p></li></ul><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-bottom-style: solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">三、创作</h2><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">1.标题</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">聚焦了话题，也明确了自己此次干货要达到的目标。那就在写文章之前，给文章想一个标题吧。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">标题决定了别人会不会点开你的文章，一个好的标题甚至可以让原来不想点击的用户也愿意点击瞧一瞧。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我个人的写标题的一些方法：</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><strong>挑选可以总结文章论点的词句</strong>：比如“不用一年读100本书，你玩主题阅读就好啦”</p></li><li><p><strong>告诉读者他能学到什么，要具体的陈述</strong>：比如“如何用30分钟读懂一本书?”</p></li><li><p><strong>暗示文章所提供的解决方案</strong>：比如“别学东学西了，先建立自己的知识体系吧”</p></li><li><p><strong>在标题中使用问句来让读者参与进来</strong>，比如“如何把“鸡汤”熬成“干货””</p></li><li><p><strong>好奇心，悬疑标题</strong>，比如“每天4点起床，半年后就当主管了”</p></li><li><p><strong>承诺所达到的效果，解释你的文章如何能为读者解决问题</strong>，比如：“从学渣到学霸-我的100天阅读简史”</p></li><li><p><strong>承诺教会读者某件事，使用“如何”或者“N个步骤”等字句</strong>，比如“绩效考核很烦人，四个步骤搞定它”</p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">建议去微博关注一些文案界的大神，比如@小马宋大V。</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">2.前言</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">干货型文章，要注入主题，在开头前言部分及明确主题。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">学会使用金字塔原理，将文章最重要的信息放到文章开头。这样大家在零碎时间进行阅读的时候，可以跟你的前言来判断是否需要深读。不管写得好不好，结论先行，能节约读者的时间，就是一篇好文章。</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">3.主体</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>逻辑</strong>：之所以能称得上是“干货”，最大的特征就是逻辑结构清晰。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">前言部分你已经抛出了你的主题和核心观点；在主体部分你就需要通过分支来解释说明咯。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/195046-fb60d30bfe966ae9.png\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\"  wp-image-278371 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/195046-fb60d30bfe966ae9.png\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577315.png\" alt=\"195046-fb60d30bfe966ae9\" width=\"729\" height=\"262\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">干货文章的金字塔原理</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>简洁</strong>：能一句话说完就别写成两句话。能画张图说明的，就不要一堆文字来解释。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">格式一致：段落和标题的格式要一致。例如在简书的写字界面:</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/195046-4c04e205236dff2b.png\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278369 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/195046-4c04e205236dff2b.png\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577365.png\" alt=\"195046-4c04e205236dff2b\" width=\"800\" height=\"140\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">各个段落标题的H1-H4的使用要统一</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">3.结尾</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>进行回顾</strong>：当你完成主题部分的书写之后，到了结尾部分。你首先需要对整篇文章进行一个简单的回顾，回顾的方式还是可以参考金字塔原理：重新阐明观点，再简要对主题部分的结构进行总结。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114049.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278372 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114049.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577395.jpg\" alt=\"QQ20160131114049\" width=\"560\" height=\"321\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">结尾进行回顾</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>不断优化：</strong>第一遍写完的文章并不是最终稿，你需要进行反复的修改和整理。特别是在你写这篇文章的时候，是在不同的时间里组装完成的时候。会出现大量衔接问题和重复。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">一篇干货足够干，不断优化起到很大作用。</p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-bottom-style: solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">四、分享</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">到这里，一篇干货型的文章总算写完了。</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>但是如何让别人知道你写了这篇干货呢？</p></li><li><p>如何去验证你写的东西对别人是否有用呢？</p></li><li><p>如何将自己的知识放到大众面前去接受批判，查漏补缺呢？</p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>1.互联网发表：</strong>简书，豆瓣，微博都是很好的网络发布平台。这些平台上发布你的文章会给你打来大量的访问量和反馈。你可以在接受反馈的过程中对自己的文章进行不断完善更新。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>2.公众号投稿：</strong>你还可以向和你的主题相关的公众号进行投稿。小编们找文章好辛苦，如果你能理解他们的难处，将文章的排版和层次结构做得很清晰，相信一定会受到他们的青睐。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>3.朋友圈</strong>：朋友圈属于自己私人底盘，跟朋友们分享自己的文章一直是一件很开心的事情。虽然我写得不够好，但是他们一直在鼓励我。相信你也在自己的圈子里获得鼓励的力量。</p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-bottom-style: solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">五、结尾：</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">每个人都有自己学霸的一面，我们明白了分享的好处之后，也说明了写文章是最适用性的分享方式。将自己的隐形知识转化为显性知识，这样的文章就是“干货”。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114153.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278376 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/QQ20160131114153.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570577465.jpg\" alt=\"QQ20160131114153\" width=\"578\" height=\"269\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">简单回顾本文</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>欢迎来到人人分享时代！</strong></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">#专栏作家#</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">彭小六，新媒体作家，人人都是产品经理专栏作家。30岁IT老处男，产品狗，铲屎官，爱阅读，爱手绘，爱自行车旅行。8年程序员经历，三次创业失败，立志成为全栈类型产品经理。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/58\\87.html', '', '0', '1549');
INSERT INTO `cms_article` VALUES ('88', '', '<blockquote style=\"width: 800px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0px; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.7999992370605px;\">接的企业网站外包项目是个坑，有时候比自身产品还难做。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.7999992370605px;\">对企业客户提供建设网站服务时，我们通常都要进行需求了解，下面对普通企业网站的需求做一个简要总结。</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/qiye1.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" size-full wp-image-278319 aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/qiye1.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570727679.jpg\" alt=\"qiye\" width=\"680\" height=\"320\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">一.大致需求</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">现有网站情况可分为：已有网站需要改版，已有网站需要新建，无网站需要新建。这对现有网站会有一定参考意义。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">企业网站的浏览群体定位最先应该有的是一个浏览群体的定位。是一般浏览者，潜在消费者，公司内部人员，求职者，还是国外用户。多数企业网站应该都是面向一般的消费者，一些有外贸性质的就要考虑到使用其他语言的用户，涉及到语言版本问题。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">网站浏览人数预估涉及到网站服务器的选择。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网站建设目的（功能定位）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">包括下面几点功能：</p><ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>企业展示宣传（主要宣传公司的环境和实力）</p></li><li><p>发布信息（通过网站了解企业最新信息）</p></li><li><p>加强与客户的沟通和交流（如产品在线咨询，销售，投诉等）</p></li><li><p>产品展示（通过网站了解产品详细信息），网络招聘（发布招聘信息）</p></li><li><p>在线商城（实现电子商务）</p></li><li><p>业务和客户管理（对业务员业绩和客户资料进行网上管理）</p></li><li><p>产品流向管理（对产品的进销库存等进行管理）</p></li><li><p>其他功能（可能的其它功能定位）。</p></li></ul><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">以上功能可以进行多选，一般企业网站基本为前五项功能定位。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网站后期运营推广</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">网站建成之后自己进行运营还是外包他人进行运营。建成后使用何种推广手段，网络广告，百度联盟还是SEO等。这是后续可能存在的附加需求。</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">二.整体需求</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网站栏目</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">功能对应栏目，比较常见的栏目有以下几个：企业简介，企业文化，企业新闻，产品展示，企业招聘，联系方式，会员中心，在线预约，在线商城等，有的还要有客户案例，服务项目等。</p><p><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/fd6cf22d9ffb920694d3ec4029a9eb6e.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/fd6cf22d9ffb920694d3ec4029a9eb6e.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570728037.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">根据栏目列出具体框架，以上是一个简单的图示。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网站布局：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">网站布局是吧每个栏目拼凑起来，通常来讲首页的布局最为重要，然后是头部logo，导航，底部是贯穿每个分页的，网站栏目和网站布局通常要用Axure等原型设计工具来完成。</p><p><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/1bb21ec934bad8a1e46bb5a0ef5cb3d2.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/1bb21ec934bad8a1e46bb5a0ef5cb3d2.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570728139.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">上面是一个简单的的网站首页布局。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网站后台：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">后台实现对所有网站内容的管理，应包括绝大多数内容的管理和控制，除了根据大概需求制作后台，还要根据下面说的细节需求进行功能制作。</p><p><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/8b102a4976468f59541ce99e9158e2f5.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\" aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/8b102a4976468f59541ce99e9158e2f5.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570728197.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">上图为简单的后台框架，此外管理员权限，网站信息设置等也要进行设计。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网站的风格</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">包括以下几类：生动活泼，清爽明快，优雅舒适，平凡中立，有冲击力，大家风范有气魄，坚实刚健，华丽高贵。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">不限于以上几类，事先可以选择三条大致说明，待到设计时在具体探讨。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网站的色调</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">包括以下几类：冷色调（蓝、紫、青、灰、有浪漫、清新、简洁等特点)，暖色调(红、黄、绿、有活泼、大方、视觉冲击力强等特点)，简洁、雅致，综合型(按不同类型由设计师设计)，其它。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">不限于以上几类，事先可以选择一条大致说明，待到设计时在具体探讨。</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">三.细节需求</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">细节需求主要探讨对象是产品设计人员和客户，一些客户可能会注重一些细节的需求，下面简要的说几个方面的细节需求。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">信息发布的需求</strong></p><ol style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>可分类显示信息，可删除、添加、修改新闻信息的类别。</p></li><li><p>可按照信息类别查询、添加、删除、修改某一条新闻信息。</p></li><li><p>新闻能够显示图片和文字，允许且只可以上传图片及压缩格式文件，新闻信息可以附带其他下载资料，如新商品的使用说明书等。</p></li><li><p>可以让某条重要信息固定出现在所有信息的最前面，也可让某条信息固定在某一类别信息的最前面。</p></li><li><p>可以显示浏览者对某条新闻信息的阅读次数。</p></li><li><p>有新闻信息检索功能，浏览者可按照信息的分类查询某条新闻信息的标题或内容。</p></li><li><p>可设置某条信息的自动发布时间和自动过期日期，系统会根据预设智能发布或撤销信息发布；</p></li><li><p>每条新闻信息有标题、副标题、作者，并能自动添加发布时间。</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">产品展示的需求</strong></p><ol style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>产品能够按照某种分类来显示，可删除、添加、修改产品的类别信息。</p></li><li><p>可按照产品类别查询、添加、删除、修改某一个产品的具体内容。</p></li><li><p>可设置推荐产品，推荐产品自动排在所有产品或某一具体产品类别的最前面，易于客户浏览。</p></li><li><p>每个产品都有缩略图和放大图，产品的介绍要包括文字介绍和图片介绍，可图文混排。</p></li><li><p>能够统计客户对某一产品的浏览量，并可按照浏览次数的多少顺序或倒序排列产品，可以统计在一段时间内某种产品被浏览的次数，从而得知客户对哪种产品更感兴趣。</p></li><li><p>有产品检索的功能，浏览者能够迅速查询到某一产品的介绍。</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">会员管理的需求</strong></p><ol style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>管理员可对会员信息进行分类查询（日期、姓名）、修改及删除。</p></li><li><p>会员可自行维护个人注册信息，可对个人注册信息进行修改和删除，如遗忘密码可在线找回密码。</p></li><li><p>可以设置会员分类，针对不同会员设置不同权限。</p></li><li><p>可以根据会员条件，用户名、公司、权限、电话等多项信息进行检索。</p></li><li><p>可以针对某类或特定的会员自动定期发送公司产品报价或其他广告信息等。</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">留言反馈的需求</strong></p><ol style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>管理员可设置浏览者是否需要注册成网站会员后才能留言。</p></li><li><p>留言要有审核功能，浏览者发布留言或咨询必须通过管理员审核方可出现在网站。</p></li><li><p>管理员可修改、删除、回复每条留言记录。</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网上招聘的需求</strong></p><ol style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>可发布招聘信息，招聘信息的内容应包括职位名称、性别要求、年龄要求、工作经验、学历等等</p></li><li><p>每条招聘信息能够设定过期时间，过期的招聘信息自动消失。</p></li><li><p>管理员可搜索、浏览、删除某份简历，对符合条件的求职者发送面试通知。</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">网上商城的需求</strong></p><ol style=\"list-style-type: none;\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>可对会员进行购物管理，有标准购物车功能（分修改、继续购物、清空、结算四个状态），可对购物车在结算之前任意步骤进行查询和修改。</p></li><li><p>购物过程支持网上结算，购买者可依据订单号查询订单状态（已收到订单、已收到货款、已发货、已送达收货人等状态）。</p></li><li><p>可在首页设定打折商品或推荐商品，可设定会员购买折扣，可对订单状态进行跟踪和管理（修改状态、删除订单）可查询当日新增加订单和所有订单。</p></li><li><p>可统计一定时段的各种商品的销售数量、发货数量、成交金额，可支持办理退单或退货手续。</p></li></ol><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这就是普通企业网站的需求分析，不是很详细，只是大体的把一些要点罗列出来了。而现实过程也更加是一个复杂的过程，需要不同职位的人分担和负责自己的任务，才能把整个需求明确并落实。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">之后的路还有更多坑等着。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/58\\88.html', '', '0', '1549');
INSERT INTO `cms_article` VALUES ('89', '', '<blockquote style=\"width: 800px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0px; border-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-style: solid; border-width: 1px 1px 1px 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28.7999992370605px;\">因为知乎用户邓棵的一篇专栏《<a title=\"看完了张小龙的 2359 条饭否日记\" href=\"http://www.woshipm.com/pmd/277371.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none;\">看完了张小龙的2359条饭否日记</a>》，微信创始人张小龙的饭否账号突然就这么被扒了出来。让我们看到了这位七星级产品经理的另一面，NB的张小龙原来也有做产品的痛苦。</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/ae1373cf2f15672dc1d25f8b3793fc14.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\"mycls aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/ae1373cf2f15672dc1d25f8b3793fc14.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570778762.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">七星级产品经理张小龙有什么做产品的痛苦？</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这两天，因为知乎用户邓棵的一篇专栏《看完了张小龙的2359条饭否日记》，微信创始人张小龙的饭否账号突然就这么被扒了出来。这个是张小龙的饭否页面。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/7936d3aa5b0b3fb0f1aa289b37c1d7b7.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\"mycls aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/7936d3aa5b0b3fb0f1aa289b37c1d7b7.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570779287.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我也专门上了一下饭否，我是饭否很早很早的用户，我的第一条饭否是2009年6月。当时饭否上有不少产品牛人，但一直没听说张小龙在上面，王兴关注了700多人，我看也没关注张小龙的饭否账号@gzallen。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">但张小龙是关注了王兴的，看来张小龙隐藏的够深。但是，张小龙已最新登陆了他的饭否并设置了隐私保护，已经看不到信息了。张小龙现在的饭否页面已经变成这样了。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><a href=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/84af6847d63c67217e9f83588b013caa.jpg\" class=\"highslide-image\" style=\"color: rgb(41, 86, 152); text-decoration: none; cursor: url(http://www.woshipm.com/wp-content/themes/woshipm-2015/images/highslide/zoomin.cur), pointer; outline: none;\"><img class=\"mycls aligncenter\" data-original=\"http://image.woshipm.com/wp-files/2016/01/84af6847d63c67217e9f83588b013caa.jpg\" src=\"/../../upload/editor/1549//1454570779528.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"margin: 5px auto; padding: 5px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 96%; height: auto; border-radius: 3px; display: block; text-align: center; background: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"/></a></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">张小龙还有一个神预测，他说：微博之后，将是推送。写于2012年3月5日。张小龙也做自我否定：一个被人预见必然会成功的产品，必然会是个失败的产品。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">当然，张小龙这个账号更像自己与自己对话，所以很真实，也很袒露心声，更多是关于人性和产皮的思考。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我发现，张小龙也有自己的心魔，NB的张小龙也有自己做产品的痛苦。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">比如，张小龙说：我在生活上不是一个有洁癖的人，但对待产品却分毫必究，介大概就是传说中的精神分裂吧。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102);\">张小龙最大的心魔应该是这句话：Think Different！（与众不同），这也是乔布斯的信条。张小龙说：Think Different！我经常用这句话来提醒自己，我没有乔老爷的才，一定不能因为要think different而走火入魔。</strong></p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">前几天，微信照片红包刷屏时，一个小米的人问我：张小龙团队是怎么脑洞大开想出这种产品的？</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">的确，微信在产品创新上，一是保持着很克制，一是保持着极致的Think Different。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“Think Different”其实也是所有产品人的心魔，一方面我们要Think Different，要打破常规；另一方面，Think Different意味未知的需求，意味新的品牌，意味着失败，我们也经常提醒自己，不要Think Different。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">为了破解这个产品心魔，张小龙有3句狠话，值得所有产品经理看3遍：</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">1、口碑！口碑！口碑！</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">张小龙：“互联网产品，好友是如何来的？必须是用户自己手把手拉来的。任何的批量好友导入，都是收效不大的。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“互联网产品应该是由用户推动，而不是产品经理来推动。产品经理的作用只是找到四两拨千斤的地方稍微用点力。”</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">2、减法！减法！减法！</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“你问我们和竞争对手比有什么区别，我说我们没有他们那些臃肿艳俗的部分。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“大部分的所谓创新，都是把问题搞复杂化而已。”</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">3、凡是以KPI为目标的领导都是不合格的！</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“整天将KPI挂在嘴上，以KPI为目标来工作的leader，都是不合格的，庸俗的，没有想法的，令人痛苦的，无法言语的。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“同意。请各部门按此落实执行。转@和菜头 公司里，凡是有老板参加的会议就拼命发言的人，凡是有抄送老板的邮件就拼命回复的人，直接炒掉根本不会影响任何业绩，而且团队的开心度上升了。”</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">痛苦才是所有创新的发动机。</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">张小龙的这些痛苦，你有什么感悟？</p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-bottom-style: solid; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">以下为@gzallen饭否摘录：</h2><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">张小龙谈自己</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">gzallen是机器人。2010-12-15 16:27</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我进到饭否就说饭否上该说的话，进到微博就说微博上该说的话，回到办公室就说办公室该说的话。我不敢说自己有想法了，想法全是环境催生出来的。2010-12-27 15:11</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我智商高的时候，情商就低。情商高的时候，智商就低。两个一样高的时候，我就双高了。2010-12-29 01:20</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">to be a better man 2011-01-21 17:50</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">这么多年了，我还在做通讯工具，这让我相信一个宿命，每一个不善沟通的孩子都有强大的帮助别人沟通的内在力量。2011-01-23 01:54</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">等我老了，我希望拥有leonard cohen的声音。2011-02-04 00:31</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我为什么能起得这么早？ 2011-02-18 10:30</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">哥喜欢的不是产品，是战争。2011-05-13 15:27</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">人要成功很难，比成功更难的是，知道自己的成功是偶然的。2011-05-13 15:28</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">Think Different！我经常用这句话来提醒自己，我没有乔老爷的才，一定不能因为要think different而走火入魔。2011-08-25 23:27</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">面试产品经理，所有技能合格后，要问，你喜欢摇滚吗。回答否的，就算了。2011-09-14 14:51</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">我在生活上不是一个有洁癖的人，但对待产品却分毫必究，介大概就是传说中的精神分裂吧。2011-09-19 21:50</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">看到和菜头爆料腾讯，那个张什么龙貌似牛X闪闪啊，有空要去拜访一哈。2011-10-19 13:12</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">石头剪刀布是我的杀手锏。mark。2011-11-04 03:04</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">多少艰苦不可告人。2012-04-01 18:43</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">张小龙写的小段子</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">此恨绵绵有时尽，花开花谢无绝期。纯拼字。2010-12-19 01:04</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">古今多少事，尽付笑谈中。如今多少花，都在风雨中。2010-12-22 02:32</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">去年今日此门中，回眸一笑百媚生。拍照秘笈。2010-12-27 16:01</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">春花秋月有时了，冬虫夏草无尽时。2011-01-17 19:46</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">你强烈反对的，一定是你自己也拥有的。---艾伦仁波切。2010-11-28 02:02</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">距离就是，你发一条微博，这条微博要途经北上广，进出九九八十一台路由器，中间还要被拆包解包合并包，被两百个CPU进行过处理，再显示在我的电脑上。而你明明坐在离我几米的地方。2010-12-22 15:54</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">古人爱月，今人爱日。古人借月抒情，今人日日抒怀。2010-12-23 18:24</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">需要多么强大的内心，才能看破红颜啊。2010-12-26 18:59</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">月亮代表我的心，意外怀孕怎么办？路边野花不要采，意外怀孕怎么办？怕什么戒律清规，意外怀孕怎么办？树上的鸟儿成双对，意外怀孕怎么办？2011-02-13 01:25</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">更快，更高，更远。不是奥林匹克，是蚂蚱。2011-02-15 23:33</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">多情之人看到情薄，多事之人看到事多。2011-02-25 01:55</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">萌是第一生产力。2011-10-15 06:29</p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 15px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; border-left-color: rgb(238, 238, 238); border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 8px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 26px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">张小龙谈产品</h3><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">还是你们用户爽，哪里爽到哪里，苦的是做互联网的，要整天分析你们的阴暗心理好让你们更爽，还不能明说。2010-11-27 23:18</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">一个产品，要加多少的功能，才能成为一个垃圾产品啊！2010-11-27 23:24</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">如果说产品做的一切都在满足用户的虚荣，热闹，逃避，贪恋等，那么，大众同样都有受虐的心理，为什么不做一款产品去虐待他们？ 2010-12-06 00:47</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">网络尚未普及的时候，产品必须依靠功能多来取胜，并且产品是自成一体的。网络普及后，才催生出一种新的产品形态：产品极简，反而有利于在网络这个大生命体中自我繁衍，并且产品是面向连接的。2010-12-15 16:03</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">好的网络产品，必然是无法预料其会不会成功的。成功的产品，刚好是“碰巧”成功了。但这个碰巧并不是创造者的运气，而是，这个产品刚好能在网络生命体中生存和繁殖。就像我们无法知道一个小孩为什么成长如此迅速一样，我们无法知道一个网络产品为什么会成功，即使做的人，也应该感谢主。2010-12-15 16:06</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">一个被人预见必然会成功的产品，必然会是个失败的产品。成功的产品是不能预见的。至少，是不能被人所预见的。机器来预见还有可能。2010-12-15 16:11</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">漂流瓶让我体会到群体的伟大：它的行为模式在我们的预想之外，我们自己也无法完全理解。如果非要分析，倾诉和期待回应（交友）还是第一位的。2010-12-16 01:56</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">让人没有成就感的是，我们随便搞一个简单的游戏，比如扔石头看谁扔得远，都会参与者众。如果再辅以按省市区排名，就会火爆。2010-12-23 14:35</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">互联网产品应该是由用户推动，而不是产品经理来推动。产品经理的作用只是找到四两拨千斤的地方稍微用点力。这方面，饭否给了个表率。这么久以来，他们只是添加了“测试版”三个字，其它什么都没变。对此，我很感动。2010-12-25 18:14</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">流通正在取代内容本身，内容变得更小更方便传播。mp3取代唱片，微博取代书本，短信取代信件。我怀疑有一天，微小的内容也没有了，大家直接通过网络交换荷尔蒙。2010-12-27 13:26</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">整天将KPI挂在嘴上，以KPI为目标来工作的leader，都是不合格的，庸俗的，没有想法的，令人痛苦的，无法言语的。2010-12-27 15:27</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">同意。请各部门按此落实执行。转@和菜头 公司里，凡是有老板参加的会议就拼命发言的人，凡是有抄送老板的邮件就拼命回复的人，直接炒掉根本不会影响任何业绩，而且团队的开心度上升了。2010-12-31 17:19</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">你问我们和竞争对手比有什么区别，我说我们没有他们那些臃肿艳俗的部分。2011-01-02 15:20</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">如果有这样一个网站，号称数据放在月球，服务器放在卫星上，太阳能供电，永久运行，100年没问题。因此，你写的任何记录都会永久保存。不知道会不会很多人去用。2011-01-04 19:31</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">每次看到我们产品中提示“xx操作已成功完成”“消息已成功发出”的“成功”二字，我就很头大，说了很多次还是出现，今天就下死命令产品中不可以再出现“成功”二字。我有文字洁癖，还是走火入魔了。“消息已成功发出”，搞得好像还有不成功发出的消息似的。2011-01-17 15:28</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">从众多的kik模仿犯来看，国内基本没有从用户心理考虑产品的产品经理。除了模仿，他们的创新也是意淫。2011-01-17 17:42</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">心有千千结，每种结都是一个产品。关系千万重，每种关系都是一个产品。未来世界，应该是每个人都会做一个十个用户的产品的时代。2011-01-18 12:41</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">在两列火车擦肩，就要相向而过的刹那，他和她掏出手机，挥舞，终于，他们交换了微x号码。广告就这么拍了。2011-02-17 00:52</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">互联网产品，好友是如何来的？必须是用户自己手把手拉来的。任何的批量好友导入，都是收效不大的。2011-05-18 03:12</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">互联网的最终目的，是让关系学见鬼去。2011-06-16 19:44</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">赞同。转@和菜头 要提防那些Blog写得好的产品经理，因为在Blog上花的时间越多，在产品上花的时间就越少。原来还以为有例外，现在看起来无一例外。2011-08-08 22:06</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">做产品，就是跟用户谈一场恋爱，否则只是一场商业交易而已。产品人是多么的博爱啊。2011-08-26 18:32</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">大部分的所谓创新，都是把问题搞复杂化而已。2011-11-07 03:48</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">人是环境的反应器。微博像是一个环境，但它不会主动刺激人，所以是个伪环境。到微博看东西是不人性的，哪有到环境里逛逛再决定做什么的，那不叫反应。而是当环境发生了点什么事情刺激到人了，人做出的行动才叫反应。所以，微博之后，将是推送。2012-03-05 02:44</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">“微博让人变傻”。今天一起吃饭的朋友也这么说。其实微博本身不会这么厉害。2010-12-14 16:30</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">他人即地狱，那么，微博是地狱的复数。2010-12-15 16:27</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">微博是洪流，看似波澜壮阔，里面都是沙子。2010-12-16 13:21</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">微博是个穿衣服的地方，饭否是个脱衣服的地方。2011-01-06 12:44</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">开复竟然写了本《微博改变一切》的书。我很佩服他竟然能就微博写出那么厚一本书出来。2011-01-11 19:33</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">微博和饭否都是蒙太奇，但微博的镜头太过花哨和表演，饭否更纪实。2011-01-15 02:01</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">饭否上能看到很多真实的情绪外泄，不像微博都是围观别人的苦难和炫耀。2011-03-06 17:16</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">新浪错失了最好的一次机会，就是做微信类东西。2011-05-21 14:41</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">突然我明白了，那些微博上收听一个人还要弹个框的烂体验，真实意图是，提高用户的收听门槛，让用户以后逐渐畏惧收听，来保持timeline的清爽。2011-07-18 18:28</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">其他每次看到知乎上人在讨论为什么启动画面是一个人顶个球，我就很乐。2011-09-20 18:08</p><p style=\"margin-right: 15px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); text-indent: 2em; line-height: 28.7999992370605px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\">人是环境的反应器。微博像是一个环境，但它不会主动刺激人，所以是个伪环境。到微博看东西是不人性的，哪有到环境里逛逛再决定做什么的，那不叫反应。而是当环境发生了点什么事情刺激到人了，人做出的行动才叫反应。所以，微博之后，将是推送。2012-03-05 02:44</p><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/58\\89.html', '', '0', '1549');

